text: Myanmardictyna is a genus of araneomorph spiders in the family Dictynidae, containing the single species, Myanmardictyna longifissum. It was first described by J. Wunderlich in 2017, and is only found in Myanmar. ==References== ==External links== Category:Dictynidae Category:Monotypic Araneomorphae genera
title: Myanmardictyna
